ABOUT HOOKS AND STRINGS
This application runs on a single page.
It includes a HTML file, CSS, JavaScript, and JSON File.
Hooks & Strings is a web application designed to cater TO crochet and knitting designers. It displays different handmade designs which can be bought.
It also allows users to give reviews.
It will allows creators to add designs and interact.
